        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="future-pharma">
      <h2>Ready to Take the Next Step in Your Career?</h2>
      <p>Join Pharma Desk today and discover endless opportunities in the pharmaceutical industry. Explore jobs, connect with experts, and build a brighter future in pharma.</p>
      <a href="/jobs" class="btn">Explore Jobs Now</a>
    </div>
  </div>
  <footer class="footer">
    <div class="footer-content">
      <div class="footer-section">
        <h3>Quick Links</h3>
        <ul>
          <li><a href="/dashboard">Dashboard</a></li>
